<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.6">
<l>periyāṉai yamarar talaivaṟkum piramaṉukkum</l>
<l>uriyāṉai yukantā ṉavaṉukku muṇarvataṉuk</l>
<l>kariyāṉai yaḻuntūr maṟaiyōrka ḷaṭipaṇiyum</l>
<l>kariyāṉai yaṭiyēṉkaṇ ṭukoṇṭuka ḷittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself the superior one,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who is difficult to realize</l>
<l>For the immortals’ leader [Indra], for Brahmā,</l>
<l>And for the one who prized the elephant skin,</l>
<l>The dark one at whose feet the Vedic experts of Aḻuntūr bow,</l>
<l rend="indent">I, his servant, was reeling!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
